Set up handler403 in your root urlconf as per: https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/2.0/topics/http/urls/#error-handling

Then in the view you can do something like:

```py
def handler403(request, exception=None):
    if isinstance(exception, Ratelimited):
        return HttpResponse('Sorry you are blocked', status=429)
    return HttpResponseForbidden('Forbidden')
```

